jun matij tkub´el ab´j ch´ixme kab´e ab´q´i t-xe: mya ikyjo tze´n jun kan, aye twitz mya tz´ok ky-q´eq, aye ky-witz mya ik kyten ik tza´n jun mascara, extzen
ya mya tb´anil Tom Riddle. Iktoq tten ik tzeʼn otoq tzʼok qʼoʼn qʼaqʼ tiʼj t-xmilal ex otoq tzʼok qʼeq tiʼj; aye t-xilen ky-q´ob´ extzen ky-b´is ky-b´is, extzen aye saq ky-witz jalin at jun ky-chik´ te jumajx
qʼonka twitza, maske aʼyeju xnaqʼtzal naʼmxtoq kypon toj t-xaq aju ojtzqiʼntoq tuʼn Harry qa aʼyeju
ok k-okil. Toktoq jun t-xbʼalun qʼeq keʼyin, ex aju twitz
ik tza´n t-spik´umal saqb´aqin n-chi t-spik´umal tib´aj t-xu´k.
A Dumbledore t-xe t-xaq u´j mya tzaj tq´o´n jun yek´b´il te t-xob´il.
