jam-packed. A kwart tzaj t-xob´il tej t-xi´ t-xo´n tib´aj jul te tilb´ilal. Ok tq´o´n twitz ti´j Dean exttzen Seamus q´uqliqe toj jun k´lojin nqayin: A jlu
t-xilen qa aju ja te q´uqb´il il ti´j tu´n tten tzqij, moqa ch´ixme. Xtix
